E2DWBA.original: ~z~They got a car all packed up and ready to go. All we got to do is take it.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~有一辆装好毒品的货车，咱们只需要抢走它。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~He showed. We been waiting on you to drive, L.
~z~We need a boat for this thing.
~z~We ain't doing it for the romantical aspect, bro. They moving shit by boat, and that's how it's gotta be took.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~又不是来拍泰坦尼克，兄弟。他们拿船运货，我们才要开船去抢。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~It's time to get paid. Let's go.
~z~We heard some major movers of product is meeting their connect.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~听说有几个毒枭在和下家见面。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~There ain't no way we can fuck this up, bro.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~这波我们不可能搞砸的，兄弟。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~One day I will and I'll have saved some of this cash for her. Anyway, these cats is holding.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~总有一天会的，我也在为了那个她存钱了。总之，这些先放放。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Thought maybe we could get into the mix of that shit and walk with the merchandise and the cash.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我们可以进去搞波事，然后带上货和钱走人。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Damn right. I'm gonna get two sets of fries. That's how rich I'm gonna be.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~太对了。薯条我也要点双份。就是这么有钱任性。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~How's it feel to slum it, bro? You driving around two low rate pushers, not some Vinewood slut.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~过苦日子的感觉如何，兄弟？带着两个小马仔出门，而不是好麦坞的臭婆娘。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~I was faster than you, wasn't I? Except in that mental arithmetic shit.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我是比你快很多。要心算的时候除外。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~What happening is we gotta get on the river and pull some piracy shit on a convoy.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~这次要乘船去抢劫一个船队。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Don't get your hands too dirty, L. How 'bout you start off simple and drive?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~别把自己惹得一身骚，L。先从简单的开车开始吧？

E2DWBA.original: ~z~We going out to get ahold of this car. It meant to be loaded up with some real pure product.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~咱们出去把这车子拿下。车上应该装了批高纯度的货。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~You such a sad cynic, bro. Don't you ever get tired of that shit?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~你怎么这么悲观啊，兄弟。天天发愁还没发腻吗？

E2DWBA.original: ~z~And then there's a chance we might get shot down, right?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~打架的时候就有可能出事，对吧？

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Okay, A. You gonna tell me what the order of the day is?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~好了，A。告诉我今天的安排是啥。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Rique, bro, you got any idea what the purpose of this outing is?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~Rique，兄弟，你能说说今天出来干嘛吗？

E2DWBA.original: ~z~You proficient at freaking out underage girls, you sad fuck.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~你恐吓未成年小女孩最熟练了，你个可怜虫。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~You know how much work it's taken to get the info to set this shit up?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~知道我要花多少工夫，才能得到最关键的货物情报吗？

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Shut up, A. You ain't got no baby.
~z~You mainly just grind away so your ass can break even. What specifically are we doing?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~一般都是辛苦半天勉强回本。我们到底要干嘛？

E2DWBA.original: ~z~But you don't need none of that when you jacking people.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~但你打劫别人的时候不用算数。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Good work, bro. Good work. Just don't get your grubby ear anywhere near me.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~干得好，兄弟。干得好。那你别拿脏兮兮的眼睛看我。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Nice of you to join us, bro. We could do with a driver. Imagine we a pair of fags from a boy band.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~你跟我们一起干真好，兄弟。有个司机真好。当我们是男孩乐队里的一对基佬吧。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~There he is. Get in, you driving.
~z~ We gonna walk in on a deal and take the cash and the product.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我们杀入交易现场，然后拿走钱和货。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~You ready to get up in the mix, L?
~z~I'm totally proficient in that shit now.
~z~That's a shame, bro. I could do with a pleasure cruise.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~那可惜了，兄弟。我还挺想乘邮轮度假的。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Ain't you a specifical little bitch? Okay, we busting open a convoy and taking their shit.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~你这逼崽子咋这么多问题？好吧，我们要截住一个车队，抢走他们的货。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~It would be if we was all rich like you, Downtown, but some of us are in this to put food in our babies' mouths.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~如果咱们像你一样有钱，那肯定的，城里人。但咱们干这些是为了养家糊口啊。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Same as it always is, L. We ripping fools off.
~z~They is two parties meeting right now. We can go in there when the cash and the shit is on the table.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~现在有两拨人在。等他们交钱交货，我们就把东西都抢过来。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Yo, L. These guys got a boat all packed with product and it's ready to go.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~哟，L。这帮人把东西都装上船准备走了。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~How long you been in this game, A? What you mean "there's no way it can fuck up"?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~你干这行多久了，A？你说「这波不可能搞砸」是啥意思？

E2DWBA.original: ~z~This exciting, homie. We gonna get to ride in a helicopter. We gonna get paid and it gonna be fun.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~这波很爽，哥们儿。咱们要开直升机，又能捞钱又有乐子。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~You funny, you real funny. I mean we taking that shit. Some fools packed it with product.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~你个逗逼，你真的逗。我是说偷过来以后。有傻逼在船上装了货。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~You want me to give you a beat? I thought you quit rapping, bro, after everyone laughed at you.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~要我来点节拍吗？我以为大家都笑话你之后，你就不敢说唱了，兄弟。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~That would a nice thing to do, wouldn't it?
~z~Some bitches got a stash we gonna raid.
~z~We got word that some guys is doing an exchange.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我们得到消息，有几个人要进行交易。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~I just happy he lavish them lessons on you, 'cause we all benefit.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我只是高兴他给你报了驾校，帮了我们大忙。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~It's Mr. Part-time. Get behind the wheel, bro.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~兼职哥来啦。上来开车吧，兄弟。
~z~好吧哥们，简简单单抢一波车。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~We moving on a stash, bro. Should collect some nice product.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我们要去偷货，兄弟。估计这次是批好货。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Cops don't take kindly to that shit. And it ain't a fun bid when you get caught.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~条子可不会对这种事客气，被抓了也不会有啥好下场。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Why don't we just go to the park or something, and chill the fuck out.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~要么去趟公园吧，大家都冷静冷静。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Maybe, but we probably gonna have to fight a load of blood hungry freaks before we get to the chopper.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~也许吧，但上直升机前可能还得和一帮嗜血的怪物打一架。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Thought maybe we could rip them off, take the money and the product.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我觉得可以干翻他们，拿上货款和毒品。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~I told you he was dependable, A.
~z~So we just walk in there and alleviate them of it? Why do I think that shit is easier to say than do?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~所以只要进去抢走他们的东西？说起来容易做起来难啊。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~There's always a way, especially when you involved.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~总有可能搞砸，这次还有你参与。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~I don't know what you talking about, man. I ain't got a boyfriend.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我不懂你在说啥，哥们。我可没有男友。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~That's the real work, the stickup's easy. Vinewood shit.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~那可是技术活，抢劫才简单。好麦坞骗人的。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~We need any running done, you the man for that.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~待会儿要追人了，就派你出去追。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Yeah, bro. That's exactly what I mean.
~z~This a good run, L. Two for one sale.
~z~What exactly am I handling, Mr Keeping-it-oh-so-real?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我要搞定什么呢，坚持真我的老兄？

E2DWBA.original: ~z~I ain't got no problem no more, L. I spent most last summer at the public pool.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我早就会水了，L。去年夏天我几乎都泡在了公共泳池里了。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Fuck you, bro. I got the down low on a stash and this is how you treat me?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~操你妈，兄弟。我给你货物的情报，你就这样对我？

E2DWBA.original: ~z~You ain't ever gonna get tired of those jokes, is you?
~z~Gonna walk away with both the money and something worth putting on the street.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~然后带着钱和街上的硬通货跑路。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Hey, L, this shit gonna be fun. We ripping off a convoy.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~嘿，L，这回很好玩，咱要去劫一个车队。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Word is people are moving some product across town.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~有消息说，有人正在城里运货。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Their motherfucking stash, bro. We taking that shit out.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~当然是他们的货，兄弟。我们统统抢走。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~So we making two sets of enemies? Sounds like the rest of my life!
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~那我们要跟两批人对着干？我下半辈子也就这样了吧！

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Oh, so you mean like, enough to go for the double Bleeder burger, and not just the single?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~哦，也就是说，够点双份的吸血鬼堡了，不是只够一份？

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Product and Profit. Two of the three Ps.
~z~There be a boat docked up with our name on it, homie.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~靠岸的船上写着咱的名字，哥们儿。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~I ain't the one with the swimming problem, A. If I were you, I'd be worried.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我又不是不会水的那个，A。我是你的话，就已经慌了。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Guys have a car all packed up with shit and it ain't even on the move yet. We just picking up a stationary vehicle.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~那帮人把货装上车了，开都没开走。我们把停着的车偷走就行。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Sugar daddy then. I don't care what you call him, L.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~那就叫干爹吧。我不在乎你怎么称呼他，L。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~It's real easy for you, ain't it L? You just show up and come along on the job.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~你倒是容易，L。你只要集合，和咱们一起干活。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~What you mean, man? It actually called, like, the Armando Moron Cruise Liner?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~啥意思，哥们？是不是叫，Armando傻逼邮轮？

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Let me take a guess. You bribed a junkie and he gave up the stash right away.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~让我猜猜。找个瘾君子塞点钱，他就全都供出来了。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~You lucky I got my ear to the streets, homie. Otherwise you wouldn't be making no money.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~幸好我在街上有眼线，哥们儿。不然你都没法赚钱。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~We ripping of some punks making an exchange.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我们要干掉几个做交易的混蛋。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Hey, I don't need no kicks. I deal with that shit from the driver's seat.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~嘿，我不需要热身。我在驾驶室就能解决他们。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Sounds like a plan, man. Here's hoping it'll all work out that simple. With you involved, how can we go wrong?
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~听上去还不错，哥们。希望执行起来也那么容易。有你在，怎么会失手？

E2DWBA.original: ~z~We gonna highjack them on the road. Take what we need and get on with our lives.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我们半路把他抢了。拿走需要的货物，然后直接跑路。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~and the cash someone was hoping to spend on it.
~z~Let's just hope they pussies too, man. That way you get your third P and we walk out of there not dead.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~希望他们的战力也是屁吧，哥们。这样凑齐三P，我们才能活着出去。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Stupid motherfuckers should keep their route more secret next time.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~这帮蠢逼下次应该对自己的路线好好保密。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Better than your anorexic chicken legs, man.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~那也比你的没肉鸡腿好多了，哥们。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~I'm afraid we getting wet, bro. Putas decided to move this shipment by boat.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~恐怕咱们要湿身了，兄弟。这帮臭逼打算用船运货。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~You gonna keep up with the big boys, L?
~z~What info you got on this shit, A?
~z~Yo A, you should watch out, man. There's all kind of germs on the street. You don't wanna catch no rat flu.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~哟，A，你小心点，伙计。街上到处是细菌，你不想得流感吧。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~These guys got a chopper all loaded with product for us to commandeer.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~这帮人有架装满货的直升机，等着咱们去抢。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~These stickups are where we actually risking our lives, bro.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~抢劫才是真正有生命危险的啊，兄弟。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~I don't know, but word is they got a car full of product and it all sounds pretty tempting.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~不清楚。我听说，有一辆车装满了货，听起来很诱人啊。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~I ain't gonna let you kill my vibe man with your cynicism. I'm looking forward to this.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~别拿你的悲观主义坏我心情。我很期待的。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Hope you got your kicks on, L. We chasing a moving target. Guys are taking a shipment across town.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~希望你热好身了，L。这次是个移动中的目标。他们想拉着货穿过城市。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Give me the rundown, H. What we doing?
~z~You think you can handle this shit, Mr. Downtown?
~z~Yeah, bro. We hitting these motherfuckers where it hurts.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~好啊，兄弟。他们哪里痛，咱就打哪里。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Figures, bro. You probably can't run on them massive jamon legs anyway.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~行吧，兄弟。我看你那双肥肉火腿确实没法跑步。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Things go to plan, there won't be no next time for these gentlemen.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~计划顺利的话，这帮人没有下一次机会了。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~I always had a problem keeping up with you, H. You got some pace man.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~我总是跟不上你，H。你走得很快。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Thank you. And I had skills by the way.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~谢了。顺便说一句，我会说唱的。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Sure bro, no doubt. I can handle that shit, or at least, I'm dumb enough to try.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~确实，兄弟，没毛病。我能应付得了。再不济，我也愿意试一试。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~No, actually I don't. Not when it improves my chances of surviving a dope run with you.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~不，确实没腻。何况跟你们一起拉货想不发愁都难。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Technically, bro, you don't get paid that often.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~严格来说，兄弟，你平常没咋赚钱。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~What we always doing, taking scores, we getting paid.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~和平常一样啊。辛苦干活，然后赚钱。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Good thing your boyfriend got you that helicopter license, bro.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~还好你男友让你考了直升机驾照，兄弟。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Ha fucking ha. I mean tell me what the fuck we doing.
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~呵呵。我意思是告诉我要去干啥。

E2DWBA.original: ~z~Same old, L. We ripping people off. Hoping to walk away from this one with something some cat's got for sale,
E2DWBA.translated: ~z~老样子，L。咱们大开杀戒，带上他们要卖的货物跑路，
